0 LORE~
Skill Type: Active
Command: lore <object>

The lore skill allows you to study an object in your inventory to
determine its properties, such as damage for weapons, armor class for armor
and other information.  Using the lore skill costs endurance equal to twice
the level of the item being studied.  Training this skill makes it more
likely to work on the first try.  
~

0 HAGGLE~
Skill Type: Passive

The haggle skill allows you to negotiate lowered prices from NPC vendors
when buying items and higher prices when selling items.  Training this skill
increases the likelihood of it triggering and the discount/bonus you can
get.  
~

0 FLAMEVOID~
Skill Type: Active, Buffing
Command: flamevoid

The flamevoid skill allows a person to become one with the Void, shutting
out distractions and giving them a bonus to hit their target in combat with
weapons and fists (not weaves).  Training this skill makes it more likely to
work, increases the bonus received and the amount of time it lasts.  
~

0 'PICK LOCK'~
Skill Type: Active
Command: pick <direction/object>

The pick lock skill is used to open doors and containers that are locked
without the key, but it can only be used to unlock something, not lock it
again.  Training this skill makes it more likely to work.  

There are some locks that cannot be picked and will require the key to open;
you will receive a message indicating that the lock is 'too complex' to be
picked in this case.  
~

